                    <span>Dont buy this book, 
<br />
<br />I will be running out to buy the Krutz CISSP Exam Prep book ASAP!
<br />
<br />Let's just say that after the first three chapters Ms. Harris's book, it became real obvious that she felt more need trying to push her agendas. Most authors have the good judgement to stay neutral using his/hers he/shes.... NOT Shon. It is quit annoying.
<br />
<br />It get's two stars. One for her ability to cut and paste information that is freely available on the internet. The second because she uses some funny illustations.
<br />
<br /></span>
                  
